|------|------|--------|-------|
| `--text-xs` | 0.75rem | 400 | Labels, captions |
| `--text-sm` | 0.875rem | 400 | Secondary text |
| `--text-base` | 1rem | 400 | Body copy |
| `--text-lg` | 1.125rem | 400 | Lead text |
| `--text-xl` | 1.25rem | 600 | Subheadings |
